# The committed evidence is evidence/report.json (canonical MC/DC truth table)
# + evidence/mcdc-predicate.json (signable in-toto Statement). The instrumented
# module, its manifest, and the raw run counters are large and reproducible.
/target
evidence/run.json
evidence/mcdc-predicate.json
evidence/scry-mcdc.instrumented.wasm
evidence/scry-mcdc.instrumented.wasm.witness.json
# Static viz site (4k+ pages, ~10 MB) — regenerated by mcdc-gate.sh, published
